{
  "stem": "7684.10",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the first time that we hear something from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, freight-- with a freight train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And were 80, 90 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they made-- the train, it had a two upstairs and downstairs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We slept down with the baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Oolah was in another train together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah, Oolah was in-- was Oolah in the train?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah, Oolah was in the train, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah, Oolah was in train, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were then-- and on the moment too Oolah had found all young people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I belonged already to the old generation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She belonged-- she was younger than I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was four or five years younger than I am, so she had a lot of young friends already.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But was, oh, also together in that train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we drove-- we went-- that took-- I think it took months that we went in this train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the train stopped, and it went farther.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't-- we had something to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They give us something to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think from of the Red Cross, was that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they give us something to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when the train stopped we run out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had some dishes to wash.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had to get some hot water from the-- how you call it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] The engine?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, from the engine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took some water-- hot water from the engine, and washed out the diapers with.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we jumped in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once we were upstair and the train started rolling, and we run quickly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we lost our place, what we had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And quickly we jumped on the train and the baby was in the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that took a long, long time--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1944. 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
